 &lt;p&gt;问题描述:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;org.apache.ibatis.binding.BindingException: Type interface com.dkx.mybatis01.dao.UserDao is not known to the MapperRegistry.

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;报错原因：缺少了 mappers 配置注册标签&lt;/p&gt;
